what_they_represent: Fossil-fuel power plants: stationary combustion plus electricity generation (typical natural gas or coal power stations)
Electricity generation units reporting emissions primarily from power generation equipment
Chemical manufacturing facility: fuel combustion plus nitric acid and petrochemical process emissions
Pulp & paper mill operations: combustion plus pulping/recovery and industrial process emissions
Underground coal mining: methane emissions released during mining operations
Cement manufacturing: fuel combustion plus calcination process emissions from clinker production
Industrial chemical manufacturing: combustion plus industrial process emissions
